<li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#возможные-осложнения">Possible complications</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#профилактика">Prophylaxis</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#прогноз">Forecast</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#какие-вопросы-нужно-задать-врачу">What questions should you ask your doctor?</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#список-использованной-литературы">•  List of used literature</a></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="waved-container-wrapper"> <div class="waved-container"> <div class="green-wave"></div> <div class="light-wave"></div> <div class="waved-container-content"> <div class="wrapper"> <h3>Other diseases in this section</h3> <ul class="related-list"> <li class="related-item"> <a class="related-item__link" href="predlezhaniye-platsenty.html"> <h5 class="related-item__title">Placenta previa</h5> <p class="related-item__text">Placenta previa is an abnormal location of the placenta in the lower part of the uterus in the region of the internal os</p> </a> </li> <li class="related-item"> <a class="related-item__link" href="lozhnyye-skhvatki.html"> <h5 class="related-item__title">False contractions</h5> <p class="related-item__text">False contractions, or Braxton Hicks contractions, are contractions that occur after the 20th week of pregnancy, do not cause significant discomfort and do not lead to cervical dilation and labor.</p> </a> </li> <li class="related-item"> <a class="related-item__link" href="istmiko-tservikalnaya-nedostatochnost.html"> <h5 class="related-item__title">Isthmic-cervical insufficiency</h5> <p class="related-item__text">Isthmic-cervical insufficiency is a pathological condition of the cervix that occurs prematurely during pregnancy, characterized by its painless shortening and expansion.</p> </a> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <hzy-kb-menu-toggle></hzy-kb-menu-toggle>





        



    @endsection